Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Frappe baru Standbakes sangat lucu! \N Enak banget~~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Kamu sudah mencobanya, Yamai-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1} Bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Iya! Rekomen pokoknya,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayo kita ke sana kapan-kapan! \N —Ya! Ayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Emm, permisi...
