Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Ada apa, Tadano-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:57.59,Yamai-san,,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(589.2,303.234)\fad(500,0)\xshad-2.875\yshad1.625} Yamai-san appears to be \N the leader of the stylish girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:03:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Ah, tidak, sebenarnya Komi-san sedang ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dia ingin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,—Hehehe... \N —Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah? Apa katamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Buat apa kamu mencatut \Nnama orang berkelas segala?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Panggil dia "Komi-sama", dasar pecundang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Jangan belagu mentang-mentang \Nduduk di sampingnya, bajingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,orang rendahan seperti kamu \Nharusnya sudah bersyukur bisa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,menghirup udara yang sama \Ndengan Komi-sama, dasar tahi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tahi, tahi, tahi, tahi, \N tahi, tahi, tahi, tahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tahi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Jadi ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tidak... tidak... tidak jadi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, begitu? Kalau begitu \Njangan bicara lagi denganku, ya?
