Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Bahkan Najimi pun tidak bisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Najimiiii!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehehe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Aku akhirnya menemukanmu, Najimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,—Heh. \N —Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, ternyata Maa-kun dan Shii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ada apa datang ke sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Habisnya... kamu pindah rumah
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,tanpa mengabari kami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.04,0:13:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maa-kun sangat kesepian, tahu, Najimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, mereka teman kecil Najimi, ya. \N Bikin kaget saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Terus?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ada urusan apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Aku ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,setelah kamu pergi, aku sadar...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Betapa pentingnya dirimu bagiku...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Maa-kun, semangat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Najimi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,jadilah pacarku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tidak bisa. Aku kan laki-laki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:51.60,Manga invert,,0,0,0,,{\pos(491.733,324.034)\i1\fs17.5\frz20.33} Cowok apa cewek \N sih ...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,—Najimi. \N —Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:14:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Aku telah... bertekad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Aku akan menjaga perasaan \Nini di hatiku selamanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:06.58,Manga invert,,0,0,0,,{\pos(74.133,124.566)\fs60} Maa- \N kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Seperti perempuan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,—Ngh! \N —Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hei... lepaskan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Najimi, aku tidak akan melepaskanmu lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Tekanan macam apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh–
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Oh, ternyata seorang gadis... gadis yang cantik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Kunci rumahku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} D– Dia barusan bilang "Kubunuh kamu!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Apa... apa niatnya sebenarnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Mungkinkah... mungkinkah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:56.29,Invert,,0,0,0,,{\pos(411.2,105.9)\c&H25242C&\3c&HF4F2FF&\bord1\blur0.375\t(5136,5887,\c&H565663&)} ＊ Imajinasi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Aku kemarin membunuh orang terakhir yang \Nmemperlakukan Najimi seperti ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i0} Dengan kunci rumahnya sendiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Itu maksud dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Igh–
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:58.25,Manga invert,,0,0,0,,{\pos(208.533,33.367)} Menatap—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayo lari, Shii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} Eh, Maa-kun? Eeh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:10.47,no border,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(573.067,256.967)\fscx107\fscy113} "Kuncimu terjatuh”{\fs22.5}  \N   itu yang ingin dia katakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:10.47,no border,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(626.4,317.634)\fscx43\fscy54} (Terdengar seperti "Kubunuh") \Ndalam bahasa jepang
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh- eh? Eeeh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa, Komi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mungkin, eh, \N mereka salah paham...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Komi-san, aku akan berteman denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Pff—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Komi-san, kamu sangat lucu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Aku benar-benar salah paham!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, ayo pulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamu mendapatkan teman kedua!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:18.96,no border,,0,0,0,,{\fs15\move(453.867,267.5,449.067,264.3,23,6446)\fscx87\fscy85}Kunci
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kita apakan kunci ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Mereka menyerahkannya ke polisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dia bersuara pada orang yang tidak dia kenal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Komi-san, kamu semakin berkembang!
